# Supplemental Specs
We will be using a Shopify API for ease of use for the customer.

The system will also have many non-functional requirements such as:
- Security 
- Reliability 
- Supportability 

The system will also contain full documentation of all use cases, system requirements, etc.

# Glossary
Event-goers: Our main actors, the customers perusing and buying tickets for COFC games

